verbose_text: Among the three nanoparticles including GA@CP (without PEI), GAI@CP and AI@CP (without PEG), GAI@CP exhibited a surface charge reversion from -22.59 +/- 3.69 mV at pH 7.4 to +5.56 +/- 2.01 mV at pH 6.8, and further increased to be +20.66 +/- 5.75 mV at pH 5.0.
